# bdgenomics.workflows

A package of single-node and distributed workflows for running [Big Data
Genomics](https://github.com/bigdatagenomics) tools using
[Toil](https://github.com/BD2KGenomics/toil).

For detailed documentation, see our [readthedocs
site](https://bdg-workflows.readthedocs.io).

## Supported workflows

* Workflows for running:
  * Copy number variant calling using [DECA](https://github.com/bigdatagenomics/deca)

## Quick Start

The latest release of `bdgenomics.workflows` can be installed using Pip
into a virtualenv. You must install
[Toil](http://toil.readthedocs.io/en/3.10.1/gettingStarted/install.html)
first:

```
virtualenv bdg-workflows

. bdg-workflows/bin/activate

pip install toil==3.10.1

pip install bdgenomics.workflows

bdg-deca
```

To install from source:

```
virtualenv bdg-workflows

. bdg-workflows/bin/activate

pip install toil==3.10.1

make develop

bdg-deca
```